Hello,

We’re having an issue this year where even when we register NamedCommands, PathPlanner will not execute them in our paths and autos. We’ve attempted to arrange our code so that named commands are being registered before the AutoBuider and auto selector are configured, But that hasn’t solved the issue for us. I’ve included a link to our code base. Any help/guidance on this would be very much appreciated.
